#: ../../source/live_trading/4-broker-adapter-and-integration.md:66
msgid "建议按「最小闭环」理解优先级："
msgstr ""
"Es wird empfohlen, die Priorität anhand des \"kleinsten geschlossenen "
"Regelkreises\" zu bestimmen:"

#: ../../source/live_trading/4-broker-adapter-and-integration.md:68
msgid "连接：`connect` / `is_connected`"
msgstr "Verbindung: `connect` / `is_connected`"

#: ../../source/live_trading/4-broker-adapter-and-integration.md:69
msgid "交易：`submit_with_ack` / `cancel`"
msgstr "Transaktion: `submit_with_ack` / `cancel`"

